com.magnet.connection

Interface ConnectionServiceConfigBean

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.magnet.config.api.EnableableConfiguration, HttpClientConfigBean

    @ConfigBean
@Named(value="ConnectionService")
public interface ConnectionServiceConfigBean
extends HttpClientConfigBean
    The default connection information for the implementation of ConnectionService.
